<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239278>
    dc:description "FIGURE 48. Galathea hydrae n. sp., holotype, female, 3.5 mm, Mozambique (MNHN-IU- 2013 - 8308). A, carapace and abdomen, dorsal view; B, sternal plastron; C, left part of cephalothorax, ventral view, showing antennular and antennal peduncles, and anterior part of pterygostomian flap; D, ischium, merus and carpus of right Mxp 3, lateral view; E, right P 1, dorsal view; F, right P 2, lateral view; G, right P 3, lateral view. Scale: A, E, F, G = 1 mm; B – D = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239278/files/figure.png" ;
